text: Dolichestola densepunctata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1942. It is known from French Guiana and Panama.BioLib.cz - Dolichestola densepunctata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1942
